		@MFC.N.9: MFC Device should NOT include any type of the most upper metal layer (ML, MT, MT3). 
		@For DRC puroposes, check not existence of any most upper metal over 77dt73.
		DEV_mfc interact ((MTOP or MT) or MT3) 
